  <tr>
    <td colspan="2"><code>--m-space-[xs|sm|md|lg|xl]</code></td>
    <td colspan="3">6px, 12px, 18px, 30px, 48px</td>
    <td colspan="3">Used for developing a visual rhythm between elements. Loosely follows <a
